playstore_details.title: Canopus OTP/MAC generator
playstore_details.description:
OTP/MAC token application
Highly secured user authentication and transaction confirmation method using rfc 6238 OTP: Time-Based One-Time Password Algorithm and MAC mechanism (Message Authentication Code).
Fully compliant with PSD2 RTS
Functions:
- Possibility to generate one-time password/code for login in web-bank
- Possibility to generate one-time password/code for payment transactions signing in web-bank.
Internet connection is NOT required.
Camera is required to scan QR (on your webbank payment page) to generate unique code to sign a payment.
playstore_details.summary: Generator of one-time passwords/codes to login & to sign payments
playstore_details.summaryHTML: Generator of one-time passwords/codes to login & to sign payments
